CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 3, 1954, pg. 27, reads: "Open for Business - R B & S Record Distributors, handling all major labels of rhythm, blues and spiritual records exclusively, have opened for business at this attractive 2014 Fifth Avenue address, where operators and dealers can phone, write or drop in for one-stop service. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Exterior of R B & S (Rhythm, Blues, & Spiritual) Records distributors, with sign in window inscribed "Open for Business April 1st," 2014 Fifth Avenue
